# FlexNetOS Workspace Agent Contract

This is the first file to read when working under `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS`.
The workspace root is a hollow orchestration area, not a monorepo. Real
implementation work belongs in independent peer repositories under `src/`.

## Canonical Repositories

- `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/yazelix`: FlexNetOS-owned Yazelix foundation repo.
- `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/meta`: FlexNetOS-owned meta repo.
- `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/envctl`: environment authority repo.
- `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/flexnetos_runner`: release runner/provenance repo.
- `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/upstream/<owner>/<repo>`: upstream evidence mirrors only.

Yazelix and meta are both organization-owned peer repos in this workspace. Do
not place them under `src/upstream/` unless creating a separate comparison clone.

